OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThe odd
OL,6,Flight shower possible at first,
OL,7,Fotherwise dry through the evening.
OL,8,FThen mostly cloudy for the rest of the
OL,9,Fnight with occasional rain spreading
OL,10,Ffrom the west.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FSome brightness along the
OL,13,Feast coast at times. Otherwise a
OL,14,Frather cloudy day with occasional rain
OL,15,Fin the morning, becoming mostly dry in
OL,16,Fthe afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
