OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FA
OL,6,Fchangeable period but often dry and
OL,7,Fbright with sunny spells. Some patchy
OL,8,Frain or a few showers possible at
OL,9,Ftimes, mainly in the west.
